 *
 * This file defines Doxygen groups for POSIX Option Groups and Options.
 * Groups with an RST anchor in posix/option_groups/index.rst use the same
 * label as that page; additional @defgroup entries exist as placeholders for
 * @ingroup tags when no RST page is published yet.  posix_option_groups.map.yaml
 * and the posix_symbols Sphinx extension correlate headers with these groups.
 *
 * No C declarations live here — this file is processed by Doxygen only.
 */

